@startuml seq-05-article-detail
' 序列图5：查看文章详情
title 查看文章详情序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "article-detail.js" as Front
participant "ArticleController" as Ctrl
participant "ArticleService" as Svc
participant "ArticleMapper" as Mapper
participant "FootprintController" as FPCtrl
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 点击文章卡片
Front -> Ctrl: GET /api/article/{id}
Ctrl -> Svc: detail(id)
Svc -> Mapper: selectById(id)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM article WHERE article_id=?
DB --> Mapper: Article
Mapper --> Svc: Article
Svc --> Ctrl: Article
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:Article}
Front -> Front: _fixUrl()拼接封面图

' 同时记录足迹
Front -> FPCtrl: POST /api/footprint/add(userId,target_type=1,target_id,snapshot_*)
FPCtrl -> DB: INSERT INTO footprint
DB --> FPCtrl: 成功
FPCtrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front --> User: 渲染文章详情页

@enduml
